{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕竹叶青受大老板之命招揽阿吉展开。竹叶青以至尊宝牌局为引子，试图以十万两银子收买阿吉，但阿吉不为所动，反而提出条件：大老板必须当面答应放过所有人，不再勉强任何人做事。竹叶青回报大老板，大老板虽怒其擅自作主，但听闻竹叶青已设下圈套后转怒为喜。竹叶青发现铁头三姨太金兰花对阿吉格外关切，推断二人是旧识，遂将金兰花与苗子兄妹一并擒获。大老板命竹叶青以珍珠和刀威胁金兰花说出阿吉来历，金兰花先以沉默应对，被割去半只耳朵后假装妥协，却在关键时刻以刀自刺胸膛，宁死不屈，痛骂大老板等人猪狗不如，最终壮烈而死。本章展现了阿吉的理想主义与金兰花的刚烈忠义，同时刻画了竹叶青的阴险狡诈和大老板的心狠手辣。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "据说一个人能拿到这副牌的机会只有万分之一，那意思就是说，就算你赌了五十年牌九，每天都在赌，能拿到这副牌的机会，最多也不会超过三十次！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "所以无论谁能拿到这副牌，运气都一定很不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "昨天晚上拿到这副牌的人，运气并不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这也正是我想说的，人事无常，又有谁能一直保持住自己的好运气？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "所以一个人若是有了机会时，就一定要好好把握住，不可放弃！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你还想说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "现在阁下的机会已来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "什么机会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "世人操劳奔走一生，所寻求的是什么？也只不过是名利二字而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "现在阁下已经有了这种机会，实在可贺可喜！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你就是竹叶青？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我姓叶，叫叶青竹，可是别人都喜欢叫我竹叶青！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "是不是大老板叫你来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "那么我也想告诉你一件事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "一个人挣扎奋斗一生，有时候并不是为了名利两个字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "除此之外，还有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "还有两个字，理想！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "理想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你想要的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我想要每个人都自由自在的过他自己愿意过的日子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "虽然有些人出卖自己，可是也有些人愿意挨穷受苦，因为他们觉得心安，受点苦也没有关系！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "真有这种人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我有很多朋友都是这种人，还有许许多多别的人也一样，只可惜你们却偏偏不肯让他们过自己的生活，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "所以怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以你们要我走，只有一个条件！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "什么条件？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "只要你们放过这些人，我就放过你们，只要大老板自己亲口答应我，绝不再勉强任何人做任何事，我马上就走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你一定要大老板当面告诉你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "一定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "十万两能不能改变你的意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "不能！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你真的愿意见大老板？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "今天我就愿意见他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "在什么地方见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "随便他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "韩大奶奶那里行不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "吃晚饭的时候好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我还没有请教贵姓大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我叫阿吉，没有用的阿吉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你已见过了阿吉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "那个人的确像是把出了鞘的刀，而且是把快刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你把他买了下来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "现在还没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "是不是因为他要的价钱太高？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我带了十万两银票去，可是我一见到他，就知道再多十倍也没有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我去的时候，桌上还堆满了银子，他非但没有碰过，甚至连看都没有看一眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他本来已经穷得连饭都没有得吃的，却还是没有把那么多银子看在眼里，由此可见，他要的绝不是这个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他要的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他只有一个条件，他要我们让每个人都过自己愿意过的日子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "这意思就是说，他要我们放手，把现在我们做的生意全停下来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我已替大老板跟他约好，今天晚上，在韩大奶奶的地方跟他见面！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你什么时候变得可以替我作主的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "没有人敢替大老板作主！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我只不过替大老板做了个圈套，让他自己把脖子套进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我跟他在外面谈判时，忽然发现了件怪事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我发现铁头的三姨太一直在里面的门缝里偷看，而且一直都在看着他，显得又紧张，又关切。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "那个女人是铁头从哪里弄来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "那女人叫金兰花，本来是淮阳一带的名妓，江湖中有不少名人，都做过她的入幕之宾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你认为她以前一定认得那个没有用的阿吉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "不但认得，而且一定是老相好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以她一定知道阿吉的来历？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "一定！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "现在她当然已经不在阿吉那里了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "已经不在了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "她在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "就在外面，和苗子兄妹在一起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你怎么找到他们的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我找遍了城里可能容他们藏身的地方，都没有找到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以你就从最不可能的地方去找？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我能想得到的，当然早已在大老板计算之中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你在哪里找到了他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我派去望风的两个人中，有一个叫大牛，虽然很机灵，胆子却很小，而且是个很顾家的男人，赚的钱一大半都要拿回家的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "所以你就想，阿吉很可能就用这一点要挟大牛，要他把苗子兄妹藏到他家里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我只想到像那么样两个大活人，总不会平空一下子失踪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "这一手阿吉的确做得很聪明，只可惜他想不到我这里还有一个比他更聪明的人！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "那也只不过因为我从来不敢忘记大老板平日的教训！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "现在我们只要先从金兰花嘴里问出他的来历，再用苗子兄妹作钓鱼的饵，还怕他不乖乖把脖子伸进来！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我只怕金兰花不肯说实话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "她是不是个婊子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你有没有见过一个真正多情多义的婊子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你有没有见过一个既不要钱，也不要命的婊子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我也没有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "这是最好的珍珠，漂亮的女人戴在身上，当然会更漂亮，就算不漂亮的女人戴在身上，也会有很多男人会觉得她忽然变得很漂亮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "你是个很漂亮的女人，可是每个女人都有老的时候！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "不管多漂亮的女人，到了她老的时候，都会变得不漂亮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "每个女人都需要男人，可是到了那时候，你就会发觉，珍珠远比男人更重要。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "这是一把刀，可以杀人的刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "不管多漂亮的女人，如果被这把刀戳在胸口里，珍珠对她就没有用了，男人对她也没有用了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "你喜欢被人戳一刀，还是喜欢珍珠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "珍珠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "你知不知道那个没有用的阿吉姓什么？叫什么？是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "只要你肯说，这些珍珠还是你的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "其实根本用不着我说，你们也应该知道他是谁！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他就是要你们命的阎王！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "你只不过是个婊子，为什么要为一个男人死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "因为只有他才是真正的男人，你们却只不过是一群连猪狗都不如的杂种，我能够为他死，我……我已经高兴得很。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他还要跟大老板见一次面，亲口答应他这条件！。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "耳朵缺了一半，还可以用头发盖住，若是鼻子少掉半个，就难看得很了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "金兰花",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "因为只有他才是真正的男人，你们却只不过是一群连猪狗都不如的杂种，我能够为他死，我……我已经高兴得很。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    }
  ],
